{"tid":1452552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:49:55.000Z","uid":163123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"009f7b8d9b11f3688ff1e5571fa1db1f931e6b1b","tid":1452552,"uid":163123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:40:00.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=f90e3abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=2235d7f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"40a63f733799292c86c10fb0c297fa03520a94a9","tid":1452552,"uid":298714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"[案例討論] 塞爾維亞人教你，咩叫禍不及妻兒，請各位參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/aJ3pKRC1zqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaJ3pKRC1zqY&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=9f423843\" target=\"_blank\">https://yout